-- FCC Said to Conclude Comcast Buy of NBC Meets Public Interest
-- B y   T o d d   S h i e l d s
-- 2010-12-23T16:22:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-23/fcc-said-to-conclude-comcast-buy-of-nbc-meets-public-interest.html
The U.S. Federal Communications
Commission has concluded Comcast Corp.’s purchase of NBC
Universal will meet the public interest with conditions,
according to two agency officials speaking on condition of
anonymity because the findings haven’t been made public.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter J. Brennan at 
 pbrennan3@bloomberg.net  